Hi [~jeagles], thanks for your reporting and contribution. I checked the source code of Tez Local Mode:

{code}
          ContainerId cId = ContainerId.newInstance(applicationAttemptId, 1);
{code}

I think it's more straight forward to fix as following at Tez than adding int-type newInstance method:

{code}
          ContainerId cId = ContainerId.newInstance(applicationAttemptId, 1L);
{code}

What do you think? cc: [~bikassaha]
